Faintly, fragilely, sparkling

876
01:03:19,096 --> 01:03:22,096
形になってゆくの
They are taking shape

877
01:03:22,096 --> 01:03:25,096
夜明けの面影に
In the trace of dawn

878
01:03:25,096 --> 01:03:30,096
