881
01:03:52,596 --> 01:03:59,096
微睡みに余白の答え
The answer in the blank space of a slumber

882
01:04:00,396 --> 01:04:06,096
白いページに色が咲いていく
Colors bloom on white pages

883
01:04:07,096 --> 01:04:13,096
息づいた景色を描き出す
Drawing out a landscape that has come to life

884
01:04:13,596 --> 01:04:16,296
All the colors I held back

885
01:04:16,296 --> 01:04:19,096
Start to gather in the hush

886
01:04:19,296 --> 01:04:22,596
“It's all right,” the first light tells me

887
01:04:22,596 --> 01:04:25,896
Sending warmth into my heart

888
01:04:26,396 --> 01:04:29,096
願いも希望も
Both wishes and hopes

889
01:04:29,096 --> 01:04:32,096
隠さなくていいんだよ
You don't have to hide them

890
01:04:32,396 --> 01:04:36,596
ほら、ありのままの私を描く
See, I'm drawing my true self

891
01:05:00,604 --> 01:05:05,104
Draw.
[Song: Draw.]

892
01:05:07,704 --> 01:05:10,604
At last, hold my true colors

893
01:05:10,604 --> 01:05:13,604
ほどけた輪郭も
Even the untied outline

894
01:05:13,604 --> 01:05:17,104
そっと、ずっと、重なって
Slowly, always, layering

895
01:05:17,104 --> 01:05:20,604
私の形になる
Becoming my shape

896
01:05:20,604 --> 01:05:23,904
静かな始まりに
At the quiet beginning

897
01:05:23,904 --> 01:05:30,104
目覚めた色を抱いて
Holding the color that awakened

898
01:05:33,504 --> 01:05:36,304
I'm drawing out my true color

899
01:05:36,304 --> 01:05:39,604
滲んだ輪郭も
Even the blurred outline

900
01:05:39,604 --> 01:05:42,604
淡く、脆く、煌めいて
Faintly, fragilely, sparkling

901
01:05:42,604 --> 01:05:46,104
形になってゆくの
It starts taking shape

902
01:05:46,104 --> 01:05:49,104
夜明けの面影を
The traces of dawn

903
01:05:49,104 --> 01:05:54,604
集めた色で描く
I draw with the colors I've gathered

904
01:05:54,904 --> 01:05:56,604
Draw it slow

905
01:05:56,604 --> 01:05:58,604
Draw it slow, draw it true

906
01:06:21,104 --> 01:06:23,104
Draw it slow

907
01:06:23,104 --> 01:06:25,104
Draw it slow, draw it true

908
01:06:27,604 --> 01:06:33,604
夢のぬくもりと
With the warmth of dreams

909
01:06:33,604 --> 01:06:40,104
指先に絵の具の匂い
And the scent of paint on my fingertips

910
01:06:40,604 --> 01:06:46,604
ありふれた朝の先には
Beyond the ordinary morning

911
01:06:46,604 --> 01:06:52,604
まだ知らない色が溢れてる
Colors I don't yet know are overflowing

912
